        <description>&lt;i&gt;Dragon Warrior II&lt;/i&gt; is an early top-down RPG that expands and improves on its predecessor, &lt;a href="/game/dragon-warrior"&gt;Dragon Warrior&lt;/a&gt;. Taking the role of a descendant of Erdrick, the player once again ventures forth in an effort to save the world.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Unlike the first game, &lt;i&gt;Dragon Warrior II&lt;/i&gt; allows the player to join forces with two other characters, a magic-using princess and a wizard-warrior prince. Also including expanded monster battles involving up to 6 creatures and a much larger world, &lt;i&gt;Dragon Warrior II&lt;/i&gt; is an important step in the evolution of the Dragon Warrior series.</description>
